This superior retail/showroom is the last available leasing opportunity in the newly refurbished Cairns Homemaker Centre located in the Harvey Norman Complex.

You can take immediate benefit from the existing operators and their current customer base, making this property the perfect location for any operator seeking to quickly establish their business or an additional second location.

The current tenancy mix ranges from Harvey Norman, Freedom Furniture  to a number of offices spaces and a proposed new café that is just currently being constructed and awaiting the new operator.
